title: Persias Asmat
text: Persias stand for Persatuan Sepakbola Indonesia Asmat ("<a href="English%20language">en</a>: Football Association of Indonesia Asmat"). Persias Asmat is an Indonesian <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Asmat%20Regency">Asmat Regency</a>, <a href="Papua%20%28province%29">Papua</a>. Club played in <a href="Liga%20Indonesia%20First%20Division">Liga Indonesia First Division</a>.
